D.4 Procedure

Step Action Parameters
1 Print seam pattern onto fabric substrate Nozzle temp: 220°C, bed temp: 60°C, speed: 30 mm/s
2 Mount sample in vacuum chamber Clamped at edges, no pre‑tension
3 Photograph at ambient pressure (baseline) 101.3 kPa, 10 images, calibration scale visible
4 Reduce pressure stepwise Steps: 80, 60, 40, 20, 10, 5, 2, 1, 0.6 kPa
